author: @Flichter
text:
Other than Bjorn, who is obviously the most qualified to be the genetic heir apparent to Ragnar, Ubbe always seemed like he had the most similarities with his father.

Early on, Ubbe felt sorta like a pretty convincing replica of Ragnar... but he was just a cheap knock-off underneath. He grew so much over the seasons and by the time everyone reunited in Kattlegat, Ubbe was a LOT more like Ragnar and Bjorn than the other sons.

Bjorn is definitely the most like Ragnar and in a lot of ways, a Ragnar 2.0 upgrade lol

The other brothers were definitely less blessed lol they each had maybe one strong trait of Rangar's, but severely lacked in the other areas like courage, honor, charisma and so many others.
